    "Chapter 3 Methodology DatasetsThis section describes the creation of the two data sets.",
    "The EA dataset is used for model pre-training, and the OM dataset is used for fine-tuning.",
    "Economic abstracts (EA)EA is comprised of 2.8 million abstracts of published Economic papers from 1900 to 2022, obtained from three repositories.",
    "The Research Papers in Economics (RePEc) repository abstracts were copied using RSync and then filtered to remove duplicate abstracts.",
